narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is an interesting class where you get to talk about books and authors you love for 2 hours,I would recommend it without reservation.
Great course to learn more about African literature. I didn't want to graduate with an African Studies major not having taken a course like this.
Absolutely.Wonderful books, these are authentic books by African authors from their perspective, classics. You will enjoy them. Great class atmosphere and Wonderful professor too!
Definitely! The books were so interesting!
Basically just sit and talk about awesome books by African writers from all over the continent. I would definitely recommend it.
